    dc:title "A revision of Eastern Palaearctic Anthobium Leach, 1819 (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae: Omaliinae: Anthophagini). II. fusculum group, and two additional species of the nigrum group" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2607314>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2607316>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2607320>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2607318>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2607322> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2607314>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–5. Habitus of Anthobium fusculum group: 1—A. fusculum (KAZAKHSTAN: Tian Shan), 2—A. altivagans (NEPAL: Telbrung Danda), 3—A. besucheti (paratype: Ghoropani Pass), 4—A. capitale (holotype), 5—A. cavicrus (NEPAL: Thare Pati). Scale bar: 1.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2607314/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2607316>
    dc:description "FIGURES 6–13. Mouthparts (dorsal view) of Anthobium fusculum group (6, 8, 10, 12—A. fusculum, 7, 9, 11, 13—A. monticola): 6–7—labrum, 8–9—mandibles (left and right), 10–11—maxilla (right), 12–13—labium and submentum. Scale bar: 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2607316/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2607320>
    dc:description "FIGURES 38–43. Aedeagus (parameral view) of Anthobium fusculum: 38: UKRAINE: Odessa, 39: RUSSIA: Rostov Area, 40: RUSSIA: Elton Lake, 41: KAZAKHSTAN: Tian Shan Mt., 42 (with sketched basal pieces of aedeagus): KAZAKHSTAN: Karatau Mt., 43: PAKISTAN: Swat. Scale bar: 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2607320/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2607318>
    dc:description "FIGURES 28–37. Abdominal segments of Anthobium fusculum group (28–32—A. fusculum, 33–37—A. monticola): 28, 33—male tergite VIII (dorsal view), 29, 34—male sternite VIII (ventral view), 30, 35—female tergite VIII (dorsal view), 31, 36—female sternite VIII (ventral view), 32, 37—female genital segment (dorsal view). Scale bar: 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2607318/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2607322>
    dc:description "FIGURE 44. Distribution of Anthobium fusculum. Black circles: material studied by the authors, white circles: previously published material not seen by authors." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2607322/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

